InstCount.tooltip: Number of instances of this lib_cell in the design

InstArea.tooltip: Total area of all instances of this lib_cell in the design

Function.tooltip: Function of the lib_cell, either shown as function_id attribute, or a more readable description (buffer, macro, latch, ...)

Purpose.tooltip: Purpose of the lib_cell, set with the set_lib_cell_purpose command.  Can be zero or more of 'power hold cts optimization'.

VtGroupType.tooltip: The threshold_voltage_group_type set by set_threshold_voltage_group_type (high_vt, normal_vt, or low_vt)

Width.tooltip: Width of the lib_cell in um

Height.tooltip: Height of the lib_cell in um

Area.tooltip: Area of the lib_cell in um2

SiteName.tooltip: Name of placement sites used by this lib_cell

SiteArea.tooltip: Size of this lib_cell, measured in number of sites
